        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装-hexo"><a href="#安装-hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装 hexo"></a>安装 hexo</h2><p>首先是创建一个新的文件夹来存放 hexo 所有文件，然后<code>hexo init &lt;path&gt;</code>这个目录。接着是迁移原有的文章，hexo 的文章默认存储在 source 目录下，所以直接 copy 原来目录的 source 到新的目录即可。</p><h2 id="安装插件"><a href="#安装插件" class="headerlink" title="安装插件"></a>安装插件</h2><h3 id="git"><a href="#git" class="headerlink" title="git"></a>git</h3><p>首先是 git page 插件。</p><pre><code>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></pre><p>接着指定自己的 git page 地址：<br><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  repo:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    github:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:hexinzhe/hexinzhe.github.io.git,master</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    coding:</span> <span class="string">git@git.coding.net:hexinzhe/blog.git,master</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>然后<code>hexo d</code>测试一下，上 git 上看看是否更新了</p><h3 id="rss"><a href="#rss" class="headerlink" title="rss"></a>rss</h3><p>接着是 rss 生成器</p><pre><code>npm i hexo-generator-feed --save</code></pre><p>填上配置<br><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">feed:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">     type:</span> <span class="string">atom</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">     path:</span> <span class="string">atom.xml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">     limit:</span> <span class="number">20</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="搜索"><a href="#搜索" class="headerlink" title="搜索"></a>搜索</h3><p>搜索非常重要</p><pre><code>npm i hexo-generator-search --save</code></pre><p>配置：<br><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    path:</span> <span class="string">search.xml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    field:</span> <span class="string">post</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
